a:50:{i:919186;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:6:"919186";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"20";s:7:"user_id";s:3:"601";s:6:"handle";s:7:"Glacial";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"266";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:457:"They would each politely bow and introduce themselves. Max &amp; Bella, Twin Huskies, demolitions experts, Buster, Doberman, Top rock breaker, under Glacial of course. Roxy, German Shepherd, One of Ponpon&#039;s girls, shares her love for the culinary arts, but not quite her skill. Sam, Greyhound, Born leader, smart and thorough, even tho hes the smallest of the group. Rusty, Great Dane, getting on in years but still has lots of fire, equipment expert. ";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1407793323";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#008aff";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14077933215";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ffffff";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:919187;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:6:"919187";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"20";s:7:"user_id";s:3:"601";s:6:"handle";s:7:"Glacial";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"266";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:229:"/me smiles proudly. &quot;With them, the operation will finally start making some good headway, and with any luck, they will spark something in the other packs and hopefully get them to come aboard as well.&quot; He says happily.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1407793384";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#008aff";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14077933833";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ffffff";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:919190;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:6:"919190";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"20";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"30";s:6:"handle";s:5:"Atria";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"692";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:313:"&quot;Well, you certainly have picked several highly qualified individuals.&quot; She looks over to Sam. &quot;I do hope you can help Glacial quell the authority issues we seem to be having.&quot; (( you might wanna copy that post into your profile because there&#039;s no way I&#039;m gonna remember it all :p ))";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1407793525";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#36d792";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14077935092";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#e6399b";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:919196;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:6:"919196";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"20";s:7:"user_id";s:3:"601";s:6:"handle";s:7:"Glacial";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"266";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:114:"Sam steps up and smiles. &quot;It&#039;s what I aim to do. You just leave that to us.&quot; ((Hehe I plan on it.))";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1407793906";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#008aff";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14077939053";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ffffff";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:919200;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:6:"919200";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"20";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"30";s:6:"handle";s:5:"Atria";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"692";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:120:"&quot;Very good. If any of you need some extra clothing for the cold, just let me know. I can call in some favors.&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1407793976";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#36d792";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14077939574";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#e6399b";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:919205;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:6:"919205";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"20";s:7:"user_id";s:3:"601";s:6:"handle";s:7:"Glacial";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"266";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:250:"/me trots over to Atria. &quot;You think I made the right call here?&quot; He asked in a bit of a hushed tone, He knows he did not talk this over with anyone, but he had a strong gut feeling on it. The dogs not to Atria and make way off the platform.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1407794082";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#008aff";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14077940807";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ffffff";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:919212;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:6:"919212";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"20";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"30";s:6:"handle";s:5:"Atria";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"692";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:192:"/me replies in a similar manner &quot;I don&#039;t see any issue with it. Installing your own team to manage a big project is a rather common tactic. The question is can they do the job?&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1407794307";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#36d792";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14077942914";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#e6399b";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:919216;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:6:"919216";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"20";s:7:"user_id";s:3:"601";s:6:"handle";s:7:"Glacial";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"266";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:89:"/me nods his head. &quot;I would not have asked them to come if they couldn&#039;t.&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1407794509";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#008aff";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14077945077";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ffffff";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:919217;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:6:"919217";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"20";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"30";s:6:"handle";s:5:"Atria";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"692";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:113:"&quot;Then we should move ahead as soon as possible yes? We&#039;ve dillydallied on setup long enough, yes?&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1407794548";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#36d792";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14077945330";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#e6399b";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:919225;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:6:"919225";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"20";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"30";s:6:"handle";s:5:"Atria";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"692";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:34:"*ignore the second &#039;yes&#039;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1407794728";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7: