11:"14077950388";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#e6399b";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:919255;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:6:"919255";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"20";s:7:"user_id";s:3:"601";s:6:"handle";s:7:"Glacial";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"266";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:66:"/me follows after her, motioning the others to follow and they do.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1407795216";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#008aff";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14077952148";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ffffff";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:919279;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:6:"919279";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"20";s:7:"user_id";s:3:"601";s:6:"handle";s:7:"Glacial";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"266";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:440:"Once they arrive at the mine, Glacial wastes no time stepping up and showing the group where everything was, what needed to be done, how it should be done and how he wanted it done, and the tight deadlines they currently had to meet. The small pack nodding attentively. Sam working alongside Glacial to best utilize each dogs talents, as well as looking to Atria for help on what direction to take which tunnels and where to begin for some.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1407796602";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#008aff";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14077966002";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ffffff";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:919295;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:6:"919295";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"20";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"30";s:6:"handle";s:5:"Atria";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"692";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:225:"/me unfurls some scrolls and points to them what deposits are where as well as known danger zones. &quot;She warily glances around, the local diamong dog pack (mostly huskies, chows, and malamutes) watches from the periphery.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1407797300";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#36d792";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14077972844";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#e6399b";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:919313;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:6:"919313";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"20";s:7:"user_id";s:3:"601";s:6:"handle";s:7:"Glacial";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"266";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:162:"/me would get hard to work, As well as the small pack. Quickly proving to be extremely effective, and hopefully lighting a fire under the tails of the local dogs.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1407798186";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#008aff";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14077981840";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ffffff";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:919317;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:6:"919317";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"20";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"30";s:6:"handle";s:5:"Atria";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"692";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:91:"/me pokes Glacial&#039;s shouler a small group of the largest of the local dogs comes over.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1407798238";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#36d792";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14077982228";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#e6399b";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:919318;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:6:"919318";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"20";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"30";s:6:"handle";s:5:"Atria";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"692";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:53:"&quot;Jus wha&#039; do you tink yer doin&#039;?&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1407798250";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#36d792";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14077982349";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#e6399b";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:919327;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:6:"919327";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"20";s:7:"user_id";s:3:"601";s:6:"handle";s:7:"Glacial";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"266";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:143:"/me would pause for a moment, then finish crushing a large rock before turning to face the dogs. &quot;Getting work done.&quot; He says simply.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1407798623";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#008aff";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14077986212";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ffffff";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:919332;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:6:"919332";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"20";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"30";s:6:"handle";s:5:"Atria";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"692";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:83:"&quot;An what jus makes you think you can &#039;do work&#039; in OUR mine eh?&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1407798706";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#36d792";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14077986906";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#e6399b";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:919351;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:6:"919351";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"20";s:7:"user_id";s:3:"601";s:6:"handle";s:7:"Glacial";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"266";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:122:"/me deadpans. &quot;The fact you are not doing any work at all in your mines, and that they are owned by my brother.&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1407798908";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#008aff";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14077989066";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ffffff";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:919372;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:6:"919372";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"20";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"30";s:6:"handle";s:5:"Atria";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"692";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:188:"&quot;We ain&#039;t said no puny poni could own us. This is our mine, and we say you best be leavin before we makes yas.&quot; (( I have been watching far too much Ork gameplay videos :p))";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1407799215";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#36d792";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14077991999";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#e6399b";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:919391;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:6:"919391";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"20";s:7:"user_id";s:3:"601";s:6:"handle";s:7:"Glacial";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"266";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:160:"/me puffs his chest and puts it to the dogs. &quot;Make me.&quot; He says simply. He has wrestled more then enough Diamond Dogs to be able to hold his own here.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1407799326";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#008aff";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14077993237";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ffffff";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:919410;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:6:"919410";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"20";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"30";s:6:"handle";s:5:"Atria";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"692";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:62:"He is going to need it, as several of them try to dogpile him.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1407799594";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#36d792";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14077995783";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#e6399b";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:919417;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:6:"919417";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"20";s:7:"user_id";s:3:"601";s:6:"handle";s:7:"Glacial";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"266";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:195:"/me was very used to this one, he has had many more try, and yes succeed, in dog piling him, Thankfully tho, he is a stallion, and gives them a powerful buck to try and knock the lot of them off.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1407799826";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#008aff";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14077998241";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ffffff";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:919420;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:6:"919420";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"20";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"30";s:6:"handle";s:5:"Atria";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"692";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:125:"Two are sent flying back by his mighty hooves, but the largest lands on him and begins trying to wrestle him into submission.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1407799875";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#36d792";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14077998595";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#e6399b";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:919429;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:6:"919429";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"20";s:7:"user_id";s:3:"601";s:6:"handle";s:7:"Glacial";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"266";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:221:"/me was much better with the one on one, and wrestles him right back, unfortunatly for the dog, Glacial was fully rested and ready for something like this. This was actually his plan B had he not gotten the team together.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1407800053";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#008aff";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14078000514";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ffffff";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:919445;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:6:"919445";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"20";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"30";s:6:"handle";s:5:"Atria";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"692";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:185:"The dog ends up locked hands to hooves with Glacial, the two of them vying for dimonance. &quot;Give up puny poni, this is my pack and my home and we ain&#039;t lettin ya have it.&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1407800197";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#36d792";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14078001810";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#e6399b";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:919451;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:6:"919451";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"20";s:7:"user_id";s:3:"601";s:6:"handle";s:7:"Glacial";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"266";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:229:"/me growls as he presses against the dog hard. &quot;It&#039;s not like I am trying to steal it from you and kick you out, we have legitimately acquired the mines, and I would like to have your help in mining them together.&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1407800336";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#008aff";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14078003347";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ffffff";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:919463;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:6:"919463";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"20";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"30";s:6:"handle";s:5:"Atria";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"692";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:59:"&quot;What&#039;s in it fer us?&quot; He presses right back";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1407800437";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#36d792";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14078004221";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#e6399b";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:919469;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:6:"919469";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"20";s:7:"user_id";s:3:"601";s:6:"handle";s:7:"Glacial";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"266";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:172:"/me holds his ground. &quot;You get to stay in your mine for one, and you get to make a profit and actually mine up this hole instead of let the spiders take it over.&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1407800599";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#008aff";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14078005974";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ffffff";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:919479;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:6:"919479";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"20";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"30";s:6:"handle";s:5:"Atria";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"692";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:89:"&quot;An why should I listen teh you?&quot; He&#039;s starting to falter in his strength.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1407800833";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#36d792";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14078008182";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#e6399b";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:919501;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:6:"919501";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"20";s:7:"user_id";s:3:"601";s:6:"handle";s:7:"Glacial";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"266";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:113:"/me narrows his eyes and pushes more, feeling that weakening. &quot;Because far worse ponies could be here.&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1407801357";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#008aff";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14078013560";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ffffff";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:919517;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:6:"919517";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"20";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"30";s:6:"handle";s:5:"Atria";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"692";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:106:"The dog grunts and loses some ground &quot;Sod off!&quot; One more good push could probably overpower him.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1407802155";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#36d792";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14078021394";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#e6399b";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:919521;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:6:"919521";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"20";s:7:"user_id";s:3:"601";s:6:"handle";s:7:"Glacial";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"266";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:147:"/me would not hesitate in giving that last good push. &quot;Then you Sod off, Because I have no use for dogs that won&#039;t earn there keep.&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1407802580";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#008aff";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14078025787";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ffffff";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:919523;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:6:"919523";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"20";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"30";s:6:"handle";s:5:"Atria";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"692";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:98:"/me smirks as Glacial overpowers the dog. &quot;Had enough?&quot; she comment to the rest of them.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1407802652";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#36d792";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14078026370";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#e6399b";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:919524;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:6:"919524";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"20";s:7:"user_id";s:3:"601";s:6:"handle";s:7:"Glacial";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"266";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:72:"/me stands tall, triumphant nodding to his own dogs to continue working.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1407802747";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#008aff";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14078027452";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ffffff";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:919527;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:6:"919527";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"20";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"30";s:6:"handle";s:5:"Atria";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"692";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:161:"/me goes over to stand next to him. Most of the local dogs start falling in with Glacial&#039;s group. &quot;Well done Glacial. That was rather impressive.&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1407802835";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#36d792";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14078028198";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#e6399b";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:919529;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:6:"919529";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"20";s:7:"user_id";s:3:"601";s:6:"handle";s:7:"Glacial";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"266";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:115:"/me blushes a bit and nods. &quot;Thanks, I did not want to force them in, I had to figure something out tho.&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1407803023";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#008aff";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14078030218";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ffffff";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:919532;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:6:"919532";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"20";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"30";s:6:"handle";s:5:"Atria";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"692";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:167:"&quot;Well, good news is we can start really getting to work. Think you can handle yourself here while I go check with the rail options I&#039;ve been lining up?&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1407803120";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#36d792";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14078031049";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#e6399b";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:919534;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:6:"919534";s:12:"cha